Class DBMaze

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.DBMaze

  • public class DBMaze
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the table in the Database - the annotations were finally not used due to a mapping file, but remained for readability. for this class - we had to serialize Maze and Solution - thus rewriting them and complex objects they have contained. NOTICE: Maze and Solution are represented as a blob - we serialized them with hibernate tools and wrote them that way.
    Author:
    Tomer,Alon
